<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/475375-is-this-a-clean-book-i-recognize-we-all">Is this a &quot;clean&quot; book? I recognize we all have different tastes and I&#39;m fine with that and not trying to &quot;judge&quot; anyone. But for me, I prefer to avoid reading: - large amounts of foul language - graphic violence - sex scenes or strong sexual innuendo. For reference, Brandon Sanderson&#39;s books are at about the right level for me in terms of &quot;cleanliness&quot;. I&#39;d really appreciate anyone giving me a quick rating. Thanks!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_475375'><a id="like_count_community_question_475375" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/475375?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">9 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F104089.Tigana">like</a></span>

