<li class='cover' id='bookCover_90661'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/90661.The_Collected_Poems_Vol_2"><img alt="The Collected Poems, Vol. 2: 1939-1962" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1347634941l/90661._SX98_.jpg" />
